#: ../../C/Camel-Book.rst:9
msgid ""
"Universally recognized nickname for the book *Programming Perl*\\, by Larry "
"Wall and Randal L. Schwartz, O'Reilly and Associates 1991, ISBN "
"0-937175-64-1 (second edition 1996, ISBN 1-56592-149-6; third edition 2000, "
"0-596-00027-8, adding as authors Tom Christiansen and Jon Orwant but "
"dropping Randal Schwartz). The definitive reference on :ref:`Perl`\\."
msgstr ""
"Larry WallとRandal L. Schwartzによる書籍『Programming Perl』(O'Reilly and Associates"
" 1991年、ISBN 0-937175-64-1。第2版1996年、ISBN "
"1-56592-149-6。第3版2000年、0-596-00027-8。著者としてTom ChristiansenとJon "
"Orwantが加わりRandal Schwartzが外れた)の、誰もが認める愛称。\\ :ref:`Perl`\\ に関する決定版リファレンスです。"
